name: HENFRENS - (7) THE MIND OF SLYME
description:
WHAT IS THIS?

We instructed an AI to “paint” a new original artwork based entirely on the metadata found in searches related to a Twitter user’s @ username -- 

Here is the seventh one:

It is a portrait of @themindofslyme

WOW, just wow. 

When you collect this 1/1 for 250TEZ,
half that amount goes right to Slyme. Boom! 
#tezosfam #gencycle #henlogic #asellisasale

It's a big price tag, but this is high tech stuff, the leading edge of creativity and consciousness, and it's a a dope piece of art -- so buy it if you like it.  

sincerely,

LOVEBUX LABS
